<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Activation Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .email_wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .email_header {
        background-color: #4caf50;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .email_body {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email_body h2 {
        color: #4caf50;
      }
      .email_body p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email_footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f9;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email_wrapper">
      <div class="email_header">
        <h1>Welcome to E-learning</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email_body">
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Welcome to our Learning Management System (LMS), inspired by some of the most famous LMS platforms like Coursera, Udemy, and Khan Academy. We are excited to have you on board!</p>
        <p>Your activation code is:</p>
        <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
        <p>Use this code to activate your account and get started with a wealth of learning resources at your fingertips.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        <p>Happy Learning!</p>
        <p>The E-learning Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email_footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 E-learning. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>If you did not sign up for this account, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
